<subSubSection id="E44919703AB432EC878909E5E8B63AF5" pageId="null" pageNumber="551" type="description">
<paragraph id="7FB9BC0D9FFC6854010FB7EDF3EBC2B7" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="A363553C03AE5DC73D22125D786D4D38" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
1 
<normalizedToken id="C7D38D7FE18B2A4484979250B8389C89" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
20-100 cm hoch. Stengel kahl oder sehr zerstreut und kurz anliegend behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="1EA71A8355F3BBE620482165D642E6A3" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
kahl oder zerstreut und anliegend behaart, 
<emphasis id="2FBEBCBD3FA9F41723B26DB10C6AA79F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="B5BA0D65B5E05EB504740117C6891783" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">3fach fiederteilig.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="00BF8A840C9ECF8A8A4281E2424B9438" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
im Durchmesser 3-4 cm. 
<emphasis id="59A2A0F026A06DE1CA04B887ECA41092" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<normalizedToken id="3AE6CE55C13F3A18AE3AB4EF36F2215A" originalValue="Spreublätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Spreublaetter</normalizedToken>
fast 
<normalizedToken id="B83A57ADBC10E55E05F4B3AD073A91C6" originalValue="herzförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">herzfoermig</normalizedToken>
in die stachlige Spitze 
<normalizedToken id="185F7AD21B38E82832CE31F9380180E7" originalValue="übergehend" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">uebergehend</normalizedToken>
; Spitze
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="78A07402A8B01FEE55D8F56CD5B7E9DF" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="4C412A7AA5EFE1394A62AAB1E8B020F1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
bis ebenso lang wie das Spreublatt. 
<normalizedToken id="AD9AD98BF4B45730D4FB24C7A4213FC1" originalValue="Zungenförmige" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Zungenfoermige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C1C195CB7AF63E0D2C2C347DC3AAB350" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Blueten</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E2E820454B1C823467BD8636BA471E8D" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">weiss</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="E0E613C4471311DF7286F23C16CA8C83" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
mit 7
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="6A8C1AA789E73B8BD22032172B397D82" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
10 deutlichen 
<normalizedToken id="9DAC85D1E0DE479CF6F8FBB2959DB2CC" originalValue="Längsrippen" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Laengsrippen</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="CF0C4FA2025A97E7CE8D1951C225BC9C" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="D69A5018FDEC7C1B00F23395DFC03697" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="8F9F2978965A163399C6A91309724EFD" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
, Sommer und 
<normalizedToken id="C7CE3F27D3971E61DC40FD3F9813AD24" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">frueher</normalizedToken>
Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B57DA871FD91237A9121EB3A9440C19" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="977B7C0FB0565EE12C2A0304E9BDE670" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="C03338EBCF5762C07F9FDCBC9A47609E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">18:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="40E0EFD6DAA4B6C590517E2C98043767" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Harling 1950), aus Afghanistan (Podlech und Dieterle 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="433412086E790C45D80D5219E9D3D830" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="62ABB759428710397036B192F5F9F15A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Trockene, lockere, 
<normalizedToken id="9659B700B3B43117973D44610C5FB8D8" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="B5D7888CD29DD8BC027F87E562FDDFB6" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="C198C2FD1407A8123D428E50FB53A941" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="31FA2A1C6DC88670E4E8868F290FE501" originalValue="Ödland" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Oedland</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D3C55C70BFD1E2D4C997A35C9B219AB8" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="24075E7EE6685978D9EE863DD9FB101A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="B06E7228B7B50C73477F697226B86FED" originalValue="Südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Spanien, 
<normalizedToken id="BC8CE3577C2D624C812AE2118855C2C0" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
, Italien, Balkanhalbinsel, 
<normalizedToken id="4FB2B54F269289BF779739D89D501979" originalValue="Südrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Suedrussland</normalizedToken>
; Kleinasien, Kaukasus. - Im Gebiet: Comerseegebiet, Bergamasker Alpen (Bergamo, Val Camonica), sonst selten adventiv.
</paragraph>
